  {
    question: "Can I generate multiple variations?",
    answer: "Yes. Use the 'Number of Variants' dropdown to generate up to 3 different versions at once. Each variation uses a different angle and hook so you can pick the best one."
  },
  {
    question: "Do you store my video or transcript?",
    answer: "We don't store your YouTube URL or the transcript permanently. The transcript is fetched in real-time, used for generation, and discarded. Your generated posts are saved to your account history if you're logged in."
